	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000957_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">Monday Morning</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Shaw</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I enclose the 
<lb/>paper with a perfect 
<lb/>host of corrections 
<lb/>I never read the 
<lb/>reports in the public 
<lb/>papers but hope 
<lb/>they were more 
<lb/>correct than "our 
<lb/>own reporters"<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000957_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>In some points he 
<lb/>has not caught the 
<lb/>idea which whether 
<lb/>it ever came out 
<lb/>or not was in 
<lb/>my own mind, 
<lb/>probably a share 
<lb/>and a very large 
<lb/>share of the blame 
<lb/>is after all my 
<lb/>own. <persName>Sir Roderick</persName>
<lb/>mentioned my 
<lb/>obligations to <persName>General 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000957_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/>Hay</persName>. I forget the 
<lb/>precise words. 
<lb/><choice><reg>W</reg><orig>W</orig></choice>ould you mind 
<lb/>adding something 
<lb/>like the last sentence 
<lb/>I mean if it is 
<lb/>right to do so<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>You see in the Times 
<lb/>this morning the 
<lb/>mistake is put on 
<lb/>my shoulders and 
<lb/>my friend <persName>Prout</persName>
<lb/>is no doubt ready 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000957_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'-->
<lb/>to swear that <hi rend="underline">corrected 
<lb/>by myself</hi> is true. 
<lb/>I having merely glanced 
<lb/>at the newspaper 
<lb/>thing &amp; pointed out 
<lb/>that it was all wrong 
<lb/>about the <placeName>Zambesi</placeName><reg>.</reg>
<lb/>After this "Save 
<lb/>me from some 
<lb/>of my friends"<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">D. Livingston</p>
<lb/><p>I believe I have drawn 
<lb/>my pen through the words 
<lb/>to be left out.</p>
			
